<plot>About Denmark's use of isolation prisons. The documentary focuses on the psychological damages and takes a closer look at whether human beings can bear being isolated. Furthermore, the film follows a voluntary experimental subject, who's put into an isolation cell to see how an ordinary person responds to isolation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?168512</url></doc>
